        Active_Execution__Busy --> Active_Execution__Idle: StopWork
        Active_Execution__Idle --> Active_Execution__Busy: StartWork
        --
        [*] --> Active_Telemetry__Silent
        Active_Telemetry__Silent
        Active_Telemetry__Reporting
        Active_Telemetry__TelemetryDone
        Active_Telemetry__TelemetryDone --> [*]
        Active_Telemetry__Reporting --> Active_Telemetry__Silent: DisableReporting
        Active_Telemetry__Reporting --> Active_Telemetry__TelemetryDone: FinishTelemetry
        Active_Telemetry__Silent --> Active_Telemetry__Reporting: EnableReporting
    }
